com.theif519.sakoverlay.Core.Fragments.Widgets

Class FloatingFragmentFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.theif519.sakoverlay.Widgets.WidgetFactory

  • public class FloatingFragmentFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by theif519 on 10/31/2015.

    A simple factory for restoring FloatingFragments from their serialized state. It works by passing in the array map, where it will obtain the LAYOUT_TAG from the map, and depending on what it is, it inflates it and passes the map to it for it handle setting itself up.
